### üèÜ REFERENCE NUMBER FORMATS ###
# Flight: GHFL{timestamp}{random}
# Hotel: GHHT{timestamp}{random}  
# Tour: GHTR{timestamp}{random}
# Visa: GHVS{timestamp}{random}
# Complete Package: GHCP{timestamp}{random}

### üìà BOOKING STATUS FLOW ###
# 1. Submitted (Initial)
# 2. UnderReview (Admin reviewing)
# 3. QuoteProvided (Quote sent to customer)  
# 4. PaymentPending (Waiting for payment)
# 5. Processing (Processing booking)
# 6. Confirmed (Booking confirmed)
# 7. Completed (Service delivered)
# 8. Cancelled (Booking cancelled)

